#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.112"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.112:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.112:0.2"
msgid "12. Kesivagga"
msgstr "12. With Kesi"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: assājānīya-javasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.112:0.3"
msgid "112. Javasutta"
msgstr "112. Speed"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.112:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Catūhi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato rañño bhadro assājānīyo rājāraho hoti "
"rājabhoggo, rañño aṅganteva saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a fine royal thoroughbred with four factors is worthy of a "
"king, fit to serve a king, and considered a factor of kingship."

msgctxt "an4.112:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.112:1.3"
msgid "Ajjavena, javena, khantiyā, soraccena—"
msgstr "Integrity, speed, patience, and sweetness."

msgctxt "an4.112:1.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi aṅgehi samannāgato rañño bhadro assājānīyo "
"rājāraho hoti, rājabhoggo, rañño aṅganteva saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"A fine royal thoroughbred with these four factors is worthy of a king. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.114"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.112:2.1"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu āhuneyyo hoti … "
"pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant with four factors is worthy of offerings "
"dedicated to the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a religious "
"donation, worthy of veneration with joined palms, and is the supreme field "
"of merit for the world."

msgctxt "an4.112:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.112:2.3"
msgid "Ajjavena, javena, khantiyā, soraccena—"
msgstr "Integrity, speed, patience, and sweetness."

msgctxt "an4.112:2.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu āhuneyyo hoti … pe "
"… anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassā”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these four factors … is the supreme field of merit for the "
"world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.112:2.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
